"title": "4354: rock",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4354",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A symbol of strength and permanence and a place where people in danger often took refuge. God is depicted as the Rock of Israel, being the strength, security and deliverance for his people.</p>\n<h2>Rock as a symbol of strength, stability and permanence</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech12:3\">ZEC 12:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job18:4\">JOB 18:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:23-Job19:24\">JOB 19:23–19:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job41:24\">JOB 41:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah1:6\">NAM 1:6</a></p>\n<h2>Rocks as places of refuge and shelter</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam13:6\">1SA 13:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam23:25\">1SA 23:25</a> <em>David's hiding-place from Saul</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job24:8\">JOB 24:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job30:6\">JOB 30:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:5\">PSA 27:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps40:2\">PSA 40:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song2:14\">SNG 2:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:10\">ISA 2:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:19\">ISA 2:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:21\">ISA 2:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa32:2\">ISA 32:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer4:29\">JER 4:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer16:16\">JER 16:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer48:28\">JER 48:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer49:16\">JER 49:16</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Obad1:3\">OBA 1:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:15-Rev6:16\">REV 6:15–6:16</a></p>\n<h2>God as a rock</h2>\n<h3>Symbolising his strength and faithfulness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:4\">ISA 26:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen49:23-Gen49:25\">GEN 49:23–49:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:3-Deut32:4\">DEU 32:3–32:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:2\">1SA 2:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam23:2-2Sam23:4\">2SA 23:2–23:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps28:1\">PSA 28:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps42:9\">PSA 42:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps62:6\">PSA 62:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps92:14-Ps92:15\">PSA 92:14–92:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:8\">ISA 44:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:12\">HAB 1:12</a></p>\n<h3>Symbolising safety and refuge in him</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps71:3\">PSA 71:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:30\">DEU 32:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:31-2Sam22:32\">2SA 22:31–22:32</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:30-Ps18:31\">PSA 18:30–18:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:2-Ps31:3\">PSA 31:2–31:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps61:1-Ps61:3\">PSA 61:1–61:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps62:7\">PSA 62:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps94:22\">PSA 94:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps144:1-Ps144:2\">PSA 144:1–144:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa17:10\">ISA 17:10</a></p>\n<h3>Associated with salvation and deliverance</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:15-Deut32:18\">DEU 32:15–32:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:47\">2SA 22:47</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:46\">PSA 18:46</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:14\">PSA 19:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps62:2\">PSA 62:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:35\">PSA 78:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:26\">PSA 89:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps95:1\">PSA 95:1</a></p>\n<h3>Associated with judgment and punishment</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa8:13-Isa8:15\">ISA 8:13–8:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:33\">ROM 9:33</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:8\">1PE 2:8</a></p>\n<h2>Other gods as rocks</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:31\">DEU 32:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:36-Deut32:38\">DEU 32:36–32:38</a></p>\n<h2>Water from the rock</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num20:8\">NUM 20:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod17:6\">EXO 17:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num20:10-Num20:13\">NUM 20:10–20:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:15\">DEU 8:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:15\">NEH 9:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:15-Ps78:16\">PSA 78:15–78:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:20\">PSA 78:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps105:41\">PSA 105:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa48:21\">ISA 48:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:3-1Cor10:4\">1CO 10:3–10:4</a></p>\n<h2>Rocks as foundations</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:24-Matt7:25\">MAT 7:24–7:25</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:47-Luke6:48\">LUK 6:47–6:48</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:13-Matt16:20\">MAT 16:13–16:20</a></p>\n<h2>Rocks in mining, quarrying and building</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:9\">DEU 8:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job28:5-Job28:6\">JOB 28:5–28:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job28:9-Job28:10\">JOB 28:9–28:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:1-Isa51:2\">ISA 51:1–51:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:29\">JER 23:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:26\">JER 51:26</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:34-Dan2:35\">DAN 2:34–2:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:45\">DAN 2:45</a></p>\n<h2>Rocks used as altars</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:20-Judg6:21\">JDG 6:20–6:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg13:19-Judg13:20\">JDG 13:19–13:20</a></p>\n<h2>Rock and burial places</h2>\n<h3>Rocks erected over graves</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:26\">JOS 7:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh8:29\">JOS 8:29</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam18:17\">2SA 18:17</a></p>\n<h3>Tombs quarried in rock</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:53\">LUK 23:53</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:59-Matt27:60\">MAT 27:59–27:60</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:46\">MRK 15:46</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa22:16\">ISA 22:16</a></p>\n<h3>Rocks used to seal caves and tombs</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh10:17-Josh10:18\">JOS 10:17–10:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh10:27\">JOS 10:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:59-Matt27:60\">MAT 27:59–27:60</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:46\">MRK 15:46</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:66\">MAT 27:66</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:2\">MAT 28:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark16:2-Mark16:4\">MRK 16:2–16:4</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:2\">LUK 24:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:1\">JHN 20:1</a></p>\n<h2>Rocky soil in the parable of the sower</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:20-Matt13:21\">MAT 13:20–13:21</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:16-Mark4:17\">MRK 4:16–4:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:13\">LUK 8:13</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:5\">MAT 13:5</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:5\">MRK 4:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:6\">LUK 8:6</a></p>\n<h2>Rocks in place-names</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg7:25\">JDG 7:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg15:8-Judg15:13\">JDG 15:8–15:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg20:45-Judg20:47\">JDG 20:45–20:47</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg21:13\">JDG 21:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam20:8\">2SA 20:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr11:15\">1CH 11:15</a></p>",
